hands_on_practices.solution:
我们有两个独立的松弛通道，其时间为
$$\tau_{rep}=k_1M^3,\qquad \tau_{CR}=k_2M^2$$
所以它们的速率相加：
$$\frac1{\tau_d}=\frac1{\tau_{rep}}+\frac1{\tau_{CR}}
=\frac1{k_1M^3}+\frac1{k_2M^2}
=\frac{k_2M^2+k_1M^3}{k_1k_2M^5}
=\frac{k_2+k_1M}{k_1k_2M^3}\,. $$
因此
$$\tau_d=\frac{k_1k_2M^3}{k_2+k_1M}\,. $$
表观指数为
$$\alpha(M)=\frac{d\ln\tau_d}{d\ln M}
=\frac{d}{d\ln M}\Bigl[\ln(k_1k_2)+3\ln M-\ln(k_1M+k_2)\Bigr]$$
$$=3-\frac{d\ln(k_1M+k_2)}{d\ln M}
=3-\frac{M\,(k_1/(k_1M+k_2))}{1}
=3-\frac{k_1M}{k_1M+k_2}\,. $$
